result.longName: Livestock Transport and Trading Company K.P.S.C.

assetProfile.longBusinessSummary: Livestock Transport and Trading Company K.P.S.C., together with its subsidiaries, purchases, transports, trades in, and sells meat products in Kuwait, the United Arab Emirates, Australia, and South Africa. It operates through Commercial, Food Processing, and Investments segments. The company offers livestock, fresh, and other meat products, as well as frozen and chilled meat products, and fresh cuts; fodders and fertilizers; and carcass. It also provides meat products, such as burger, meatball, sausage, minced meat, mortadella, pastrami, kabab, roast beef, and frankfurter. In addition, the company engages in the import and export of livestock; establishment and management of commercial and industrial projects; and sea transportation of miscellaneous goods. Livestock Transport and Trading Company K.P.S.C. was incorporated in 1973 and is headquartered in Kuwait City, Kuwait.
